Datasets Used
Restaurant Data

Source: Zomato + OpenStreetMap

Includes:

Restaurant location

Cuisine types

Ratings

Pricing data

NGO Data

Source: Public NGO directories

Includes:

NGO locations

Donation capacity

Service areas

Municipal Solid Waste Data

Source: Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC)

Includes:

Ward-level waste statistics

Household distribution

Waste generation trends

Geospatial Data

Pune ward boundary shapefiles

Geolocation coordinates

