Quick Start
Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/AyanJinabade/Data-Analyst.git
cd Data-Analyst
Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
Generate Synthetic Data
python synthetic_data_generator.py
Train ML Model
python src/train_xgb.py
Run API
uvicorn src.api.app:app --reload
Start Dashboard
streamlit run frontend/streamlit_app.py

Impact

This system enables:

Faster NGO food collection

Reduced food waste

Optimized donation logistics

Data-driven decision making

Potentially helping cities recover thousands of meals daily.
